TintCase-black.title: TintCase™️ Privacy Case (With Warranty) -black
TintCase-black.description:
CONCEAL YOUR PRIVACY The TintCase™️ has a tempered and tinted front screen that cannot be viewed from the sides. It's also touch sensitive! The case is also magnetic so it's easy to put your phone in and take it out. 
 If you worry people are invading your privacy or personal space, this is for you. This is for
- School Students
- Office Workers
 - People out in Public

Reviews.title: Would Recommend
Reviews.body: Order was sent out very quickly and arrived in great condition! It feels super nice and low profile on my phone which I like. Case is also magnetic and you can't see the screen from the sides just like the Tiktok video
Reviews.name: Jonny Putnam

Reviews.title: Awesome Product!
Reviews.body: i have a little trouble because sometimes i dont put much pressure on the screen and it doesnt register but other than that the case is really good i like it
Reviews.name: lopez

Reviews.title: VERY GOOD VERY NICE
Reviews.body: Bought a couple for the fam, they all loved them and thought they were pretty cool. That would be cool if yall come out with more colors.
Reviews.name: Larry Nitzsche

Reviews.title: Worth the money
Reviews.body: Arrived packaged well and is just like the tiktk videos, didn't think the quality would be as good as it is.
Reviews.name: Arnaldo O'Hara

Reviews.title: Feels Cheap
Reviews.body: I like it very much! Just like the vids on tiktok!
Reviews.name: Colin Schaden

Reviews.title: I love it!
Reviews.body: Well packed in great condition, if u have an iPhone and have problems with taking it out a phone case, this one will solve those problems because it's magnetic!
Reviews.name: Margarita Koelpin

Reviews.title: This Case Slaps!
Reviews.body: That's the second time I 've bought. I recommend it 100%. I work in a confined space with alot of people so it eases me up abit.
Reviews.name: Elliott Lueilwitz
